OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776985387
OL,3,CMan sentenced for making over 200
OL,4,Cabusive 999 calls
OL,6,FA man who harassed and berated police
OL,7,Fcall handlers when he dialled 999 over
OL,8,F200 times has been sentenced.JNone of
OL,9,Fthe calls 37-year-old Charlie Murphy
OL,10,Fmade to police were to report an
OL,11,Femergency.
OL,13,FInstead, he wasted valuable police
OL,14,Ftime, potentially delaying a response
OL,15,Fto someone who truly needed the help
OL,16,Fof emergency services.
OL,18,FBeginning on 8 June 2025, Murphy swore
OL,19,Fat and threatened call handlers as
OL,20,Fthey made attempts to ensure he was
OL,21,Fsafe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
