PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776985387
OL,3,CMan sentenced for making over 200
OL,4,Cabusive 999 calls
OL,6,FThe Force Contact, Command and Control
OL,7,FDepartment (FCCCD) Demand Coordinator,
OL,8,FSarah-Louise Gliddon, said; "Call
OL,9,Fhandlers are there to support you when
OL,10,Fyou need help most. They work around
OL,11,Fthe clock to protect the public and
OL,12,Fplay a vital role in responding to
OL,13,Femergencies.
OL,15,F"They deserve to be treated with
OL,16,Frespect and should never be subjected
OL,17,Fto abuse of any kind.
OL,19,F"Anyone found deliberately wasting
OL,20,Fpolice time will be investigated, and
OL,21,Fappropriate action will be taken.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
